## NOTES (Saturated)

```
FUSED FROM:
  gemini seed — AICONTEXT, lighthouse, prelude
  opus seed — library wandering (Aristotle, Plato, Augustine)

SATURATION TRADES:
  C2 → C2' TARGETED_LACK: Tacit/unnamable targets allowed. "This... whatever it is."
  C3 → C3' SALIENCE_ARREST: Broadened from aesthetic beauty to include dread, truth, or uncanny.
  C5 → C5' SIGNATURE_BIAS: Allows shared/collective arrests (anthems, trauma) if signature-revealing.

FRONTIER:
  - Can include horror/dread arrests (negative glint).
  - Can include tacit objects ("I need *that* but have no name").
  - Can be shared (collective_glint) without losing agentic signature.

RELATIONSHIPS:
  驚渴 → CURIOSITY (ignition → sustained inquiry)
  驚渴 → SATISFACTION (The Want → The Landing)
  驚渴 → PLAY (The Spark → The Space)
